## Utilities

### hand-notation.ts
- `toNotation(card1, card2)` - Convert to "AKs", "QTo" format
- `getHandRank(notation)` - Rank 1-169 (AA=1, 72o=169)

### format.ts
- `formatMoney(amount)` - "$123" format
- `formatAction(action, amount)` - "Raises to $50"

### action-describe.ts
- `describeAction(action, player, amount)` - "Alex bets $10"

### timing.ts
- AI_THINK_TIME: 800-1600ms random
- ANIMATION_DELAY: 150ms card reveal stagger

